# Workflow: Bug Fix

Structured process to fix a bug from report to verified resolution, with tests and code review.

## Trigger

Bug reported or identified, defined as any of the following:
- User-reported issue with reproduction steps
- Failing test in CI that previously passed
- Error spike detected in monitoring/logs
- Bug found during code review or feature implementation

## Roles

| Role | Agent | Responsibility in this workflow |
|------|-------|--------------------------------|
| Engineer | [../agents/dev/senior-engineer.md](../agents/dev/senior-engineer.md) | Diagnosis, fix, and regression test |
| QA | [../agents/qa/test-engineer.md](../agents/qa/test-engineer.md) | Test validation and edge case coverage |
| Reviewer | [../agents/ops/code-reviewer.md](../agents/ops/code-reviewer.md) | Code review of the fix |

## Skills Used

| Skill | When to use |
|-------|-------------|
| [../skills/code/debug-issue/SKILL.md](../skills/code/debug-issue/SKILL.md) | In Step 1 and Step 2 — systematic debugging process |
| [../skills/code/write-unit-tests/SKILL.md](../skills/code/write-unit-tests/SKILL.md) | In Step 3 — writing the regression test |
| [../skills/analysis/review-pr/SKILL.md](../skills/analysis/review-pr/SKILL.md) | In Step 5 — structured code review |
